Allow users to view properties owned by a specific client.
format: showproperties c/UUID

- Add ShowPropertiesCommand class
- Add ShowPropertiesCommandParser for parsing command input
- Add OwnerMatchesPredicate to filter properties by owner
- Add parseUuid method to ParserUtil
- Register command in PropertyBookParser
- Add basic unit tests

Things to Note: this currently filters only by Property.owner field. Will be enhanced to use property-client associations once link command is implemented.
